<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>登录验证码</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'PingFang SC', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.4;
      color: #333;
      background: #f8f9fa;
      max-width: 460px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 12px;
    }

    .email-container {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      padding-bottom: 12px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
    }

    .title {
      color: #222;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .greeting {
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }

    .main-content {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #555;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .verification-card {
      background: #f9f5ff;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 16px 0;
      border: 1px solid #10b981;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .verification-code {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #10b981;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      margin: 12px 0;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    }

    .expiry-notice {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #888;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    .login-info {
      background: #f8fafc;
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 16px 0;
      border-left: 3px solid #3b82f6;
    }

    .info-item {
      margin: 6px 0;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #555;
    }

    .info-item strong {
      color: #333;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .security-notice {
      background: #fffbeb;
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 16px 0;
      border-left: 3px solid #f59e0b;
    }

    .security-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #d97706;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .security-notice ul {
      padding-left: 18px;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }

    .security-notice li {
      margin-bottom: 3px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #555;
    }

    .help-text {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
      margin: 16px 0;
      padding: 10px;
      background: #f8f9fa;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding-top: 14px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #999;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .support-link {
      color: #10b981;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .support-link:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    p {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    p:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <!-- 头部 -->
    <div class="header">
      <h1 class="title">登录验证码</h1>
    </div>

    <!-- 问候语 -->
    <p class="greeting">您好！</p>

    <!-- 主要内容 -->
    <div class="main-content">
      <p>我们收到了您登录 Monie 账户的请求。</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 验证码卡片 -->
    <div class="verification-card">
      <p>请输入以下验证码完成登录：</p>
      <div class="verification-code">
        {{verificationCode}}
      </div>
      <div class="expiry-notice">
        此验证码将在 {{expiryMinutes}} 分钟后过期
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 登录信息 -->
    <div class="login-info">
      <div class="info-item"><strong>登录账户：</strong>{{userEmail}}</div>
      <div class="info-item"><strong>请求时间：</strong>{{requestTime}}</div>
      <div class="info-item"><strong>登录地点：</strong>{{location}}</div>
      <div class="info-item"><strong>设备信息：</strong>{{deviceInfo}}</div>
    </div>

    <!-- 安全提示 -->
    <div class="security-notice">
      <div class="security-title">安全提示</div>
      <ul>
        <li>请勿将验证码分享给任何人</li>
        <li>Monie 工作人员永远不会向您索要验证码</li>
        <li>如果您没有请求登录，请立即更改密码</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- 帮助文本 -->
    <div class="help-text">
      <p>如果您没有请求登录，请忽略此邮件或立即联系我们的支持团队。</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 页脚 -->
    <div class="footer">
      <p>此邮件由 Monie 系统自动发送</p>
      <p>需要帮助？请联系 <a href="mailto:{{supportsEmail}}" class="support-link">{{supportsEmail}}</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>